Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点唯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其一  圣诞…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:15.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小时候）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候的姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为「圣诞节」是「圣诞亲」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧  祝你圣诞…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叮叮当  叮叮当  铃儿响叮当
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在驯鹿的雪橇上…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难为情的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点唯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其二  紧身裤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:01:04.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小时候）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:00:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候的姐姐连袜子都没法穿好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:09.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（现在）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在连穿紧身裤都没问题了 一想到这…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让人泪流满面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.07,0:01:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点唯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其三  迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:37.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小时候）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经在新年参拜的时候迷过路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧  不要放开姐姐的手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然会迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:04.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（现在）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧～  这是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来接我～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而是姐姐经常迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完


